description:
Event Info: Join us for an exciting session where we’ll dive deep into the latest Fortnite Creative and Unreal Editor for Fortnite updates, celebrate our amazing community, and give you the inside scoop on new features that will change the way you create. Expect engaging walkthroughs, pro tips, and live interactions with our development team—all designed to level up your creative process.

This stream, we'll be chatting all about Physics with special guest NoahUEFN and more:
 - Overview of Physics
 - Tools Walkthrough
 - Build Live w/ NoahUEFN
 - Future Plans
 - Final Q&A
title: Physics | Creating in Fortnite

author: Unreal Engine
description:
Accurately visualizing all the forests, roads, and rivers that surround large-scale infrastructure projects requires the processing of an enormous amount of data. 

Watch this video and find out why AFRY turns to Unreal Engine to handle vast geometric detail for real-time visualization, and how it helps project stakeholders make better informed decisions.

Find out more about visualizing architecture and infrastructure projects with Unreal Engine here: unrealengine.com/uses/architecture

#InfrastructureVisualization, #Archviz, #AFRY, #UnrealEngine, #UE5
title: AFRY uses UE5 to visualize heavy datasets for large infrastructure projects
